Package com.google.common.base.internal

Class Summary
Finalizer Deprecated. FinalizableReferenceQueue is an unsound mechanism for cleaning up references, because (1) it's single thread can be easily overloaded, and (2) it's insistance on running a background thread is problematic in certain environments.
